Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.05,0:00:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Day 1 ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.43,0:00:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Zero trades.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.02,0:00:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Zero profit.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.36,0:00:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}And I learned more than 7 days of paper testing ever taught me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.19,0:00:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I can't code.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.67,0:00:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}9 years in crypto.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.85,0:00:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}7 days ago I asked AI to build me a trading bot.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.10,0:00:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I put a thousand down for this experiment — if it works, any ordinary person can use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.03,0:00:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}This is Day 1 of AI trading my thousand dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.86,0:00:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Today it trades with my real money for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.55,0:00:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}One word in the config — paper to live — real money starts.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.29,0:00:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I changed it, and stared at the Enter key for 20 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.46,0:00:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Then this thought hits me — if this loses everything tonight, how do I tell anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.15,0:00:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}That thought, in paper mode, never once crossed my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.29,0:00:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Not once.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.78,0:00:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I pressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.24,0:00:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Nothing happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.76,0:00:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}One hour, no trade.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.92,0:00:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Two hours, still nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.04,0:01:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}It was waiting for a signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.92,0:01:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I was waiting for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.53,0:01:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}By hour three my eyes hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.18,0:01:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}So I washed dishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.39,0:01:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Halfway through the sink, I realized I'd relaxed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.35,0:01:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Something had shifted.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.11,0:01:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I couldn't have told you what.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.15,0:01:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Day 1.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.29,0:01:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Zero trades.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.90,0:01:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}But most of what I learned all week came from those three hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.93,0:01:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Day 2 tomorrow — it actually traded.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.86,0:01:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Follow if you want to see what happened next.
